Two love children of the late Afro pop legend and musical genius Robbie Malinga have spoken out for the first time since his passing in 2017. The two adult children, whom Malinga sired before his marriage to Ann, let the cat out of the bag after the Southern African Music Rights Organisation (Samro) kept them waiting for almost a year to pay them their share from Malinga's royalties. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD